#: ../../../../../CMake/vtkModule.cmake:199
msgid ""
"The `vtk.module` file is parsed and used as arguments to a CMake function "
"which stores information about the module for use when building it. Note "
"that no variable expansion is allowed and it is not CMake code, so no "
"control flow is allowed. Comments are supported and any content after a `#` "
"on a line is treated as a comment. Due to the breakdown of the content, "
"quotes are not meaningful within the files."
msgstr ""

